@@ -0,0 +1,12 @@
+# Multi-face media review
+
+When an upload contains more than one detected face, it enters the
+`pending` review state and is withheld from publishing until a creator
+approves it.
+
+## States
+
+- `pending` — needs creator approval
+- `approved` — cleared for publishing
+- `blocked` — rejected by a reviewer
